                    <h2 style="color: rgba(234, 173, 37, 1);">OUR VISION</h2>

                    <p>We, the Youth Movement Against Alzheimer’s, envision a united effort that bridges together both the youth and elderly in a common goal to combat Alzheimer’s Disease through active fundraising and advocacy in communities nationwide.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

